@jennybacolina:

you should always look for a trusted uploader first, like DeGun said. They are those with the skulls ;-)
Also, don't feel like u are somehow morally obliged to seed after your dl is complete. This is your choice alone. Get acquainted with the whole thing first, THEN decide whether and how long u want to seed for others. Of course, without people seeding after the download, there would be no pirate bay but don't forget that there are also certain risks involved if you seed too much, depending on the country where u live and the measures you take to protect your privacy (like VPN, e.g.). Take it easy!
